{"tid":875737,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"還原自拍真面目 iOS 12.1 將修正「自動美顏效果」Bug","createTime":"2018-10-25T05:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T01:31:23.000Z","uid":215574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fd18ed297357f661dbcf935dd4941b585c1e65","tid":875737,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"當 iPhone XS 和 iPhone XS Max 上市後，很多用戶都表示自拍時，相機會自動加入美顏效果，將皮膚的瑕疵自動移除。有用戶表示這功能無法關閉，令他們無法以真面目示人，Apple 當時否認在相機加入預設修圖功能，坊間則以「Beautygate」去形容今次事件。<br />\n事隔接近一個月後，Apple 終於開腔解畫，原來所謂「Beautygate」和預設美顏修圖功能，通通都是一場誤會，自拍相片加入類似柔鏡效果是軟件有 Bug 所致。Apple 指出在 HDR 相片合成時，部份用作合成的照片欠缺細節，導致最後的相片有執走瑕疵的感覺。Apple 表示這個 Bug 將會在稍後推出的 iOS 12.1 更新中修復，而這個修正據說已經在日前推出的 Beta 版出現，之後會引進到正式版。"},{"pid":"1afdad48fe29c831688d571d0f2f3f4a507fab19","tid":875737,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"影得蒙都要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6eb3b545e9eef1142e19792c4f652ab4e208b3","tid":875737,"uid":25952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"幾時整埋比xs xs max 用主camera 影人像mode啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc25c2799983d284644b322edd0c9e4dae98eea","tid":875737,"uid":64275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec6eb3b545e9eef1142e19792c4f652ab4e208b3","tid":875737,"uid":25952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"幾時整埋比xs xs max 用主camera 影人像mode啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:31:23.000Z","msg":"xr有 xs無真心on9"}]}